  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate a new critical pathway (use of guideline-based patient
      identification criteria and for those who meet these criteria, use of dalbavancin) for the
      treatment of ABSSSI compared to usual care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
